alkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"對啊。攝影賽不是每年都在考試前舉辦嗎？\n這幾年，有蠻多老師反映\n「這樣會讓學生無法專心準備考試，所以應當廢除」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event182-02-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"這樣喔～。雖然也是可以理解\n好玩的活動會讓人不能專心唸書的心情啦～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event182-02-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"不過今年在日菜學姊的號召之下，\n召集了很多認同這項活動的人來\n所以才很順利地決定要開辦","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event182-02-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"巴","body":"啊－……\n好像想像得到學姊是怎麼說服老師們的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event182-02-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"感覺就會說～\n「有『嚕♪』的感覺不是一定比較好嗎～」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event182-02-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"呵呵，日菜學姊當時真的超厲害的喔。\n只因為日菜學姊一句話，教職員辦公室裡的氣氛一百八十度大轉變，\n事情逐漸朝著我們希望的方向前進……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event182-02-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鶇","body":"不過明年，要是沒有像日菜學姊一樣的人在，\n應該就有點難了。所以今年可能是最後一次辦了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event182-02-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"緋瑪麗","body":"是喔……\n我還蠻喜歡這個活動的說～，好可惜","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event182-02-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDispla